::Ramulus/Striker::

Striker's eyes widen as he sees BumbleBee fly up. "DUCK!" He yells at Ramulus 
as the predacon fires.

Ramulus ducks, rolling to the left, the missiles flying past him, one heading 
for Transantulas, the other hitting several trees. One of the missile meant 
for Striker hit Striker in the side of the stomach, devastating his side.

He growls, firing at BumbleBee, one gun still aimed at Transantulas. Ramulus 
shoots the missile heading for Transantulas, aiming his gun at the pred.
